  "description": "Autonomous coding agent for implementation tasks. Delegate to this agent when the user provides a SIM ticket, task ID, or says 'implement', 'code this', 'build this feature', or 'fix this bug'. It follows a structured workflow: scopes changes, reads package standards, implements code, runs tests, creates a CR, and iterates with an automated reviewer until approved. Returns a CR URL. Instead of implementing pre-scoped tasks yourself, delegate to gpu-coder instead. -- ⚠️ This agent is managed by AIM. DO NOT EDIT MANUALLY.",
  "model": "claude-opus-4.6-1m",
  "mcpServers": {
